                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>April 27, 1854</date>.</p>\n            <p><sic><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leaser</addressee></sic>, Esq.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <placeName>Phila.</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Dear Sir.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">By the present we beg to<lb/> hand you our card for the purpose to\n                call your<lb/> attention to the fact that it would perhaps be of<lb/> some benefit\n                to you to confide us your agency for the<lb/> sale of your books, such as bibles\n                &amp;c &amp;c.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">As regards to our <del>ch</del>\n                <sic>caracter</sic> &amp;c we beg to refer<lb/> you to <persName>Miss. Bernhimer\n                    Brother D</persName>, with which<lb/> gentlemen our <persName role=\"author\">Mr.\n                        Thalmessinger<add>?</add></persName> has been as<lb/> Bookkeeper for the\n                last 3 ½ years.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Mr. Isaac Bernhimer</persName> being at your place at\n                present<lb/> you may perhaps find an <sic>oportunity</sic> to speak to him<lb/>\n                about this subject.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Hoping to receive your favor as soon as possibly we are    Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">Yours very Resps.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\"><persName role=\"author\">Thalmessinger<add>?</add></persName> &amp;\n                    <persName role=\"author\">Benedict</persName></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3m03zh7d/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
